00:01:58.840 --> 00:02:07.240
later today. Now, let's move to lower-risk MDS. This is now kind of complex three. What is good

00:02:07.240 --> 00:02:13.160
that these days we have Luspartacept approved, we have Imetelstat approved. So this is all exciting

00:02:13.160 --> 00:02:20.700
because it does provide opportunity to treat mainly patients with anemia and also give therapeutic

00:02:20.700 --> 00:02:22.360
agents for patients who have MDS.

